==English==
===Noun===
'''interferometer'''
#{{physics}} any of several [[instrument]]s that use the [[interference]] of [[wave]]s to determine [[wavelength]]s and wave [[velocities]], [[measure]] small [[distance]]s, and determine [[refractive indices]]
